            "id": 5966642,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 燦星旅(2719)大漲7.05%，報40.25元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>燦星旅(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2719:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2719\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2719-TW</a>)08日09:46股價上漲2.65元，報40.25元，漲幅7.05%，成交211張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>燦星旅(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2719:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2719\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2719-TW</a>)所屬產業為觀光餐旅，主要業務為旅行業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲11.9%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.2%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-46 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-46 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：+38 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5966642",
